<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fiction-n">fiction <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fɪkʃn/    美 /'fɪkʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] (虚构) 小说：</strong></h4>
<p>反 non-fiction </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>historical / romantic / <strong>science fiction</strong>
历史/爱情/科幻小说</p></div>

<h4 id="2c">2.<strong>[C] 虚构的事；谎言：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>For years he managed to keep up the fiction that he was not married.
多年来他一直设法给人一种未婚的假象。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>fictional /'fɪkʃənl/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fictional characters
虚构的人物</p></div></div>